    "Further, in the case that b δ ≤ δ+ν µ, x 3 will coincide with x 1 in the limit as ξ → 0, and in the case that b δ > δ+ν µ, x 3 will coincide with x 2 in the limit as ξ → 0.With one further condition on DV = DV --DV + (as defined in (2.11),(2.12)), we can characterize the local stability of these DFE.Theorem 2.5.",
